      • close

        default void close()
            throws java.io.IOException
        Description copied from interface: POITextExtractor
        Allows to free resources of the Extractor as soon as it is not needed any more. This may include closing open file handles and freeing memory. The Extractor cannot be used after close has been called.(允许在不再需要提取器时立即释放其资源。这可能包括关闭打开的文件手柄和释放内存。调用关闭后无法使用提取器。)
        Specified by:
        close in interface java.lang.AutoCloseable(在界面中关闭java.lang.AutoCloseable)
